-- China's Agbank may issue preference shares in Sept or Oct -exec
-- By Engen Tham and Li Qi
-- Tue Sep 02, 2014 04:47AM EDT
-- None



SHANGHAI, Sept 2 (Reuters) - Agricultural Bank of China Ltd <601288.SS><1288.HK>, China's third largest listed lender, is contemplating issuing preference shares in September or October this year, Xu Duo, a senior official at the bank, said on Tuesday.

He made the comments at a press conference in Shanghai.